# Doraplexis Project Structure

This Flutter app follows a clean architecture with the following structure:

## Entry Points
- [lib/main.dart](mdc:lib/main.dart): Main entry point of the application
- [lib/app.dart](mdc:lib/app.dart): App configuration and routing

## Feature Screens
- [lib/screens/home_screen.dart](mdc:lib/screens/home_screen.dart): Main container with navigation
- [lib/screens/women_health_screen.dart](mdc:lib/screens/women_health_screen.dart): Menstrual cycle tracking
- [lib/screens/fashion_expense_screen.dart](mdc:lib/screens/fashion_expense_screen.dart): Fashion expense tracking
- [lib/screens/storage_organizer_screen.dart](mdc:lib/screens/storage_organizer_screen.dart): Item storage management

## Widget Organization
- [lib/widgets/cycle_tracker_widget.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/cycle_tracker_widget.dart)
- [lib/widgets/expense_chart_widget.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/expense_chart_widget.dart)
- [lib/widgets/pie_chart_widget.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/pie_chart_widget.dart)
- [lib/widgets/reminder_card_widget.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/reminder_card_widget.dart)

## Domain Layer
- [lib/models/](mdc:lib/models/): Data models
- [lib/providers/](mdc:lib/providers/): State management

## Data Layer
- [lib/repositories/](mdc:lib/repositories/): Data repositories
- [lib/local_storage/](mdc:lib/local_storage/): Local storage implementation